      • ACTION_CLIENT_GET_STATUS

        public static final java.lang.String ACTION_CLIENT_GET_STATUS
        Intent to request the client status. The result is received via an Intent having the following extras:
        • EXTRA_CLIENT containing the client package name.
        • EXTRA_STATUS containing the boolean status of the client. True means that the client is activated, else the client is not activated.
